.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

Color: azure, brown, fuchsia, apricot, amber
Nationality: egyptian, mexican, russian, australian, spanish
Beverage: lemonade, iced-cola, 7up, cola, almond-milk
Cigar: azuremaster, old-henry, vegafina, swisher, bolivar
Pet: guinea-pig, rabbit, turtle, mouse, rat
1. Nationality:egyptian == Color:fuchsia
2. Nationality:swedish == Pet:turtle
3. Nationality:mexican == Beverage:cola
4. Color:brown is on the left of Color:apricot
5. Color:brown == Beverage:iced-cola
6. Cigar:vegafina == Pet:rabbit
7. Color:amber == Cigar:old-henry
8. Beverage:7up is in the middle
9. Nationality:australian is on the far left
10. Cigar:bolivar is on the left or right of Pet:guinea-pig
11. Pet:rats is on the left or right of Cigar:old-henry
12. Cigar:azuremaster == Beverage:lemonade
13. Nationality:russian == Cigar:swisher
14. Nationality:australian is on the left or right of Color:azure
15. Cigar:bolivar is on the left or right of Beverage:almond-milk

.:: Answer ::.
